                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4040" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0989</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10328 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信“揽入”Gorenje：一场没有大股东的要约收购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hisense Acquired Gorenje List Company: An Tender Offer without  a Big Shareholder</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘素，李云霞，陈志军</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">竞标；要约收购；内部人控制；收购程序；2019百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">bidding; offer acquisition; insider control; acquisition procedure</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国企业前些年相对盲目的“扫货”式海外收购行为和中国买家“土豪”的姿态，以及收购后陷入“不愿管”、“不会管”或“不敢管”的局面，曾一度引发舆论对中国企业海外收购合理性的质疑。事实上，中国企业的海外收购正在悄然发生着改变。本案例真实再现了海信如何通过全面要约收购在斯洛文尼亚、波兰两地上市的Gorenje公司的整个过程。中国企业既要学会去尊重当地的收购规则，更要深入去研究这个规则，最后才能让这个规则为己所用。海信并未过多向媒体披露的收购设计、实施中的所思所为才是本次收购成功的关键所在。学习和分析本案例对提升和反思中国企业的国际化经营具有重要的借鉴和启示作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The relatively blind “scavenging” overseas acquisition behavior of Chinese enterprises in the past few years and the attitude Chinese buyers’ tryrant attitude, as well as the dilemma situation of “unwilling to manage”, “unable to managing” or “afraid to manage” after the acquisition, have once aroused public doubts about the rationality of overseas acquisitions for Chinese enterprises. In fact, overseas acquisitions by Chinese companies are quietly changing. This case truly reproduced how Hisense acquired Gorenje listed company listed in Slovenia and Poland through a tender offer. Chinese enterprises should not only learn to respect the local acquisition rules, but also study the rules in depth, and finally make the rules for their own use. The design and implementation of the acquisition that Hisense did not disclose much to the media is the key to the success of the acquisition. Learning and analyzing this case has the extensive applicability and practical significance for promoting and reflecting on the internationalization of Chinese enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《国际企业管理》、《国际市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理，国际企业管理，国际市场营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-10</td>
                            </tr>
